---
title: Easy Louisiana Yoghurt Chicken with Roast Veggie Israeli Couscous & Smokey Aioli
description: There’s nothing better than chicken that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully charred with mildly smokey spices and
yoghurt on the outside. That’s how we’re preparing our protein tonight, complete with wholesome Israeli couscous to
double down on all that flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
